            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288393</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>三星於美國加州聖荷西的 Galaxy Unpacked 發佈會上，正式揭曉 Galaxy S25 Edge，此機型為 Galaxy S25 系列的新成員。該款手機以其極致纖薄的設計成為亮點，機身厚度僅 6.4 毫米，比標準版 Galaxy S25 的 7.2 毫米更薄。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288398" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e1-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e1-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Galaxy S25 Edge 採用時尚銀色外觀設計，並配置兩顆後置鏡頭，與 S25 系列其他型號的三鏡頭配置有所不同。雖然目前官方尚未公佈鏡頭規格及內部硬件詳細資訊，但預期會與其他 S25 機型一樣，內建先進的 AI 功能。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288397" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e3-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e3-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>整個 Galaxy S25 系列以強化 AI 功能為核心，包括 Galaxy AI 平台及基於 Android 15 的全新 One UI 7 介面，致力於提供更個性化及情境感知的使用體驗。</p><p>至於 Galaxy S25 Edge 的定價及上市詳情，預計將於稍後公佈。</p><h2>完整現場評測影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_65535"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bUmxSmrvRHI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2></h2><p>來源: <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/22/24349658/samsung-galaxy-s25-edge-photos-unpacked">the verge</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/s25-edge-slim/fun-tech/">三星 Galaxy S25 Edge 正式發佈：不是叫 S25 Slim 厚度為 6.4mm</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
