            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288091</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 近年趨向愈來愈早推出旗下年度首部旗艦手機，由二月底到二月初，去到今年更早至一月底就發佈新一代的 Galaxy S25 系列。早前 Edward 就有幸提早試玩 3 部全新 Galaxy S25 系列的新機，現在就讓筆者與 unwire.hk 讀者們分享一下這部全新旗艦，尤其是 S25 Ultra 的初步體驗感受吧。</p><h2>完整現場評測影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_37185"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bUmxSmrvRHI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>S25 Ultra 設計向 S25 / S25+ 靠攏感覺更「一家人」</h2><p>今代 Samsung 推出的全新 Galaxy S25 系列，與上代一樣依然設有 Galaxy S25、Galaxy S25+ 及 Galaxy S25 Ultra，早前傳聞的 Galaxy S25 Slim 就暫時仍未見到實機。至於設計方面，整個 S25 系列新機與上代分別不算太大，機面及機背依然採用強化玻璃製造，不過玻璃就用上較新的康寧 Gorilla Glass Victus 2，對機身耐磨度及耐用性有更佳效果。熒幕方面，S25、S25+ 及 S25 Ultra 就分別配置了 6.2 吋、6.7 吋及 6.9 吋熒幕，由此可見前兩者熒幕未有增大，但 S25 Ultra 就比上代加大了 0.1 吋。還有一點大家可以留意到，就是今代 S25 Ultra 在機身設計上感覺進一步向 S25 / S25+ 靠攏，相比上代 S24 Ultra 採用更方角的設計，今代 S25 Ultra 角位改回圓角風格，雖然與 S25 / S25+ 相比依然較為方角，但相比上代 S24 Ultra 肯定是較圓角，筆者上手感覺沒有了上代機角的「刺手掌」手感，握在手上使用手感更加理想。另外，今代似乎機身更薄更輕，尤其是 S25 Ultra 的體驗更是明顯，加上 S25 Ultra 的熒幕邊框比上代更窄，因此今代雖然熒幕增大了 0.1 吋，但機身闊度沒有明顯擴闊，所以單手操控仍然問題不大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新一代的 Samsung Galaxy S25 系列旗艦手機剛剛推出，依然設有三部機款，分別是 Galaxy S25（左）、Galaxy S25+（上）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（右）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲設計方面，Galaxy S25（左）、Galaxy S25+（中）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（右）的熒幕及機背同樣採用強化玻璃保護，採用的是較新的 Corning Gorilla Glass Victus 2。另外，熒幕尺寸分別為 6.2 吋、6.7 吋及 6.9 吋，當中 S25 Ultra 採用較幼熒幕邊框，因此可以保有與上代相近尺寸同時，熒幕比上代大了 0.1 吋。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身設計風格上，Galaxy S25 及 S25+ 大致與上代差不多，而 S25 Ultra 就比上代採用相對較圓角的設計，風格上向 S25 及 S25+ 靠攏，感覺更像「一家人」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身邊框方面，S25 及 S25+ 依然用上鋁金屬物料，而 S25 Ultra 就仍然用上鈦金屬物料。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手感方面，由於三機設計趨於一統，所以手感亦十分相似，當然機身較細的 Galaxy S25（第一張）及 S25+（第二張）在單手操控上最為舒服，而 S25 Ultra（第三張）雖然機身較大，但今代比上代更輕薄，所以單手操控仍沒有大問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25（第一張）、Galaxy S25+（第二張）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（第三張）在單手握機操控及打字也沒有太大問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲作業系統方面，依然用上以 Android 15 為基礎而設計的 OneUI 7.0 作業系統。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
